00:37.542 --> 00:39.667
It was his mother
who got Craig killed.

00:40.792 --> 00:43.375
You made a decision. Right?

00:44.000 --> 00:44.875
Right?!

00:45.458 --> 00:47.041
-(GRUNTS)
-What?!

00:47.291 --> 00:48.458
MAGGIE: Richard has to go.

00:48.542 --> 00:50.125
He showed his ass tonight,

00:50.375 --> 00:52.375
