-(argument continues)

05:11.250 --> 05:13.000
Jennifer:
Brit! Nice to see you.

05:13.083 --> 05:15.667
-(door shuts)
-Britney: Morning, ma'am.

05:15.750 --> 05:17.709
Hey, Danny. Is Cate home?

05:17.792 --> 05:19.000
