17:14.000 --> 17:15.625
Here. Help me.

17:18.667 --> 17:20.542
-You got the glue on?
-Uh-huh.

17:24.959 --> 17:27.208
-Do you like me like this?
-What do you mean?

17:27.291 --> 17:30.667
-Um...
-Like this, like a guy.

17:30.750 --> 17:33.041
I don't know. I mean, no.
I mean, I-I don't know.

17:33.125 --> 17:35.125
Are-are you still you?

17:44.417 --> 17:46.208
-(puts down jar)
-(sighs)

17:48.667 --> 17:50.792
-(knocking)
-(conductor speaking Italian)

17:50.875 --> 17:53.250
Fuck, fuck, fuck.

